*bacula-7.4.0-r1 (23 Jun 2016)

  23 Jun 2016; Thomas Beierlein <tomjbe@gentoo.org> +bacula-7.4.0-r1.ebuild:
  Let bacula-dir start successful under systemd (Bug #584442)

  Change systemd's bacula-dir.service so that bacula-dir is run as
  root:bacula.
  While not perfect from a security point it makes bacula under systemd
  compatible with OpenRC environment.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0_rc1

